# Website (Astro)

## Stack

- **Astro** + **Tailwind CSS** — `src/`, build to `dist/`
- Minimal JS (mobile nav inline script in Header only)
- Use `<Image />` from `astro:assets` when adding photos (not needed for SVG logo in public/)
- Legacy static site in `site/` is deprecated — do not edit

## Brand (until launch)

- **Primary display name:** Logo Clothing Shop (header logo)
- **Bridge line:** "Becoming Stitch & Stone Co." (header) / footer intro line
- **SEO `<title>` pattern:** `{Page} | Logo Clothing Shop · Soon Stitch & Stone Co.` (via `site.seoTitleSuffix` in BaseLayout)
- **Do not** lead with Stitch & Stone Co. alone in `<title>` until full rebrand go-live

## Colors (tailwind.config.mjs)

- Navy `#0A2540` — primary CTA, links, footer
- Warm gray `#F5F2ED` — page background
- Stone `#D2C8B6` — cards, borders
- Gold `#C9A66B` — accents, thread dividers (not primary buttons)

## Positioning

- Gifting-first homepage and CTAs
- Primary CTA: **Plan a Gifting Program** → `/contact/`

## Copy rules

- Human, warm, professional
- **No em dashes** in customer-facing copy
- Michigan / Detroit / Birmingham when relevant

